##ob与mysql表现形式不一致
select dayname('1995.02.28')+2000000000000000;
dayname('1995.02.28')+2000000000000000
2e15
Warnings:
Warning	1292	Truncated incorrect DOUBLE value: 'Tuesday'
##经过和山庭老师确认,此处是by design的，mysql有时候会根据外层表达式，改变内层表达式的返回值，比如这里dayname外面是加一个int，那dayname会返回是一周的第几天，而不是一个字符串
select dayname('9999-12-31 23:59:59.999999')+0;
dayname('9999-12-31 23:59:59.999999')+0
0
Warnings:
Warning	1292	Truncated incorrect DOUBLE value: 'Friday'
select dayname('9999-12-31 23:59:59.999999')-0;
dayname('9999-12-31 23:59:59.999999')-0
0
Warnings:
Warning	1292	Truncated incorrect DOUBLE value: 'Friday'
select dayname('9999-12-31 23:59:59.999999')*1;
dayname('9999-12-31 23:59:59.999999')*1
0
Warnings:
Warning	1292	Truncated incorrect DOUBLE value: 'Friday'
select dayname('9999-12-31 23:59:59.999999')/1;
dayname('9999-12-31 23:59:59.999999')/1
0
Warnings:
Warning	1292	Truncated incorrect DOUBLE value: 'Friday'
