##运算符验证
##算数运算符
##当前使用表达式进行运算时,结果与MySQL5.7不一致，MySQL会以工作日索引进行计算（周一到周日对应0-6）,mysql有时候会根据外层表达式,改变内层表达式的返回值,ob无论如何都为0；
select +dayname('2022-09-07');
+dayname('2022-09-07')
Wednesday
select dayname('2022-09-07')-dayname('2022-09-07');
dayname('2022-09-07')-dayname('2022-09-07')
0
Warnings:
Warning	1292	Truncated incorrect DOUBLE value: 'Wednesday'
Warning	1292	Truncated incorrect DOUBLE value: 'Wednesday'
##比较运算符
##当前使用表达式进行运算时,结果与MySQL5.7不一致，MySQL会以工作日索引进行计算（周一到周日对应0-6）,mysql有时候会根据外层表达式,改变内层表达式的返回值,ob无论如何都为0；
select dayname('2022-09-07') = dayname('2022-09-07');
dayname('2022-09-07') = dayname('2022-09-07')
1
select dayname('2022-09-07') <> dayname('2022-09-07');
dayname('2022-09-07') <> dayname('2022-09-07')
0
select dayname('2022-09-07') < dayname('2022-09-07');
dayname('2022-09-07') < dayname('2022-09-07')
0
select dayname('2022-09-07') != dayname('2022-09-07');
dayname('2022-09-07') != dayname('2022-09-07')
0
select dayname('2022-09-07') > dayname('2022-09-07');
dayname('2022-09-07') > dayname('2022-09-07')
0
select dayname('2022-09-07') >= dayname('2022-09-07');
dayname('2022-09-07') >= dayname('2022-09-07')
1
select dayname('2022-09-07') <= dayname('2022-09-07');
dayname('2022-09-07') <= dayname('2022-09-07')
1
select dayname('2022-09-07') <=> dayname('2022-09-07');
dayname('2022-09-07') <=> dayname('2022-09-07')
1
select dayname('2022-09-07') in ('monday','Tuesday','Wednesday','Thursday','Friday','Saturday','Sunday');
dayname('2022-09-07') in ('monday','Tuesday','Wednesday','Thursday','Friday','Saturday','Sunday')
1
select dayname('null') in ('monday','Tuesday','Wednesday','Thursday','Friday','Saturday','Sunday');
dayname('null') in ('monday','Tuesday','Wednesday','Thursday','Friday','Saturday','Sunday')
NULL
